reviewText:
Delivered on Time.
Was what I was told and wanted.  Great !!!!
Packging was very good.
3 of my favorite movies, perfect price
It is nice that you can order older movies together in a set like this and they are still good quality at a lower price. Fun movies. Quick delivery.

Dvd's came in excellent condition. Love the idea of so many good movies of same genre in a smaller space - my dvd library is getting crowded. Easy to order, easy to pay, good price. Will be ordering similar products in the future.
One-stop girl's night in. Got to be good!
The quality of these movies was only second to brand new! I would purchase from this seller again in a minute!
Since I am working overseas I watch alot of movies and these are great for a night in.  I have friends that borrow them even.
YOU CAN'T BEAT THE PRICE.  IF YOU LIKE CHICK FLICKS, THIS IS A VERY GOOD COLLECTION.
